Package emissary.parser

Class FillingNIOParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • emissary.parser.SessionParser
      • emissary.parser.NIOSessionParser
        • emissary.parser.FillingNIOParser
  • public abstract class FillingNIOParser
extends NIOSessionParser
    Encapsulate the behavior necessary to slide a window through a channel and parse sessions from it. nextChunkOrDie will load the next region.
